creator: Preqin Mobile
descriptionHtml:
Preqin Pro data available anytime, anywhere. Access key alternative assets data, profiles and contact information for investors, fund managers, funds and consultants.
Ideal for investor relations, marketing and business development professionals wanting private equity, venture capital, private debt, real estate, infrastructure, natural resources or hedge fund intelligence and contact information away from the office.

The new Preqin Mobile app offers you a flexible way of accessing data whenever you need it. On a conference call, road trip, at a conference, or if you just want key data and news away from your desk – the app contains wider and more granular data on all key private market participants at your fingertips.

Available data includes;

• Investors: Assets & allocations, past investments, future plans, strategic preferences and asset class-specific contacts.

• Fund Managers: Investment preferences, fund portfolios, track records, investors, deals & assets, ESG and key contacts.

• Funds: Fundraising, performance, strategic preferences, terms & conditions and service providers.

• Consultants: Current clients, assets advised, services and key contacts.

This new app is designed for investment professionals looking for quick access to data normally only available on Preqin Pro. Packaged in the same structure as the desktop version and optimized with an intuitive mobile interface, we make it easier for investment professionals to access Preqin’s trusted data anywhere, anytime.

Preqin Mobile is only available to Preqin Pro subscribers. Any questions, problems or feedback? Get in touch at info@preqin.com.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The new version of Preqin mobile come with;
- All alternative asset class data that includes private equity, venture capital, private debt, real estate, infrastructure and hedge funds
- Preqin Pro profile structure
- News feed
- Preqin Insights
- UI enhancements
